headline: Rockwell Automation to Present at Oppenheimer 20th Annual Industrial Growth Conference
summary: MILWAUKEE, April 24, 2025--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) Vice President, Investor Relations and Market Strategy, Aijana Zellner, will present virtually at Oppenheimer 20th Annual Industrial Growth Conference on Thursday, May 8, 2025.
